values: hi! well lastnight i updated so its in here as 2day.. but um i went to bed around 5 this morning.. me n becca were crazy lastnight 8-).. then i woke up around 10:30 n went back 2 sleep til like 12.. then my mom n dad decided to leave 2day to come home instead of tomoro.. so i cleaned & stuff.. chloe started puking 3 times n it was grossss(we left it for jake to clean up, hahah) thenn meya and jessie n cory came over and swam n layed out.cory went n got us wendys.. but then they left & i realized it was already 7 so i made dinner alllll by myself.. i was proud. well now my mom n dad are home n they drove home allies new car.. a red outty. its really cute.. but im gonna go so bye!*

well.. 2day i didnt do nething but then i showered & got ready then monica came over 4 a lil bit.. then we went to the mall//movies.. we probably saw the gayest movie ever :-* umm.. then we stayed outside for a lil bit after thenn walked over to dicks 2 see alisha and BARRY came!! woo.. we madeout twice. haha jk.. thenn alisha took me home & lindsey came over.. n we watched hitch & ordered pizza.. then she went home at like 1:30 n nowwwww me n becca are sitting here, she creeps me out bcuz she says ppl are in the house, now i feel like im being watched :-[ k well bye!*

another boring night in the house.. 2day i went to monicas after my parents left for boston for a few days.. n we went to dairy queen n monica got chinese.. but then jake picked me up around 7 and came home n he left for a meeting then brought me home a frosty.. n then we watched the pacifier. noww im watching the andy milonakis show. woooooooooooo =) but uh.. ok bye.

I've learned that goodbyes will always hurt, pictures never replace having been there, memories good or bad will always bring tears, words cant replace feelings, the truth will always kill, people will always remember how you made them feel, & sometimes things you want the most you just cant have...

hey.. welll 2day wasnt the best day. some ppl make me sorta just sad the way they act & if they have something against u, why dont they just tell you? ohwell.. i guess. 

2day i didnt do nething at all but clean & shower... then ate dinner & after that i went out and played basketball with my brother jacob & we played around the world and he def. won that game.. then we  played p-i-g and i def. won that game.. hehe. im sweet at it :).. thenn i started shooting from the pool area the little steps goin up to it and me n him both got 8 shots and it was like a mile away from the hoop.. i didnt make it but he made it on his 7th try :( oo well then meya came n her n allie went on the trampoline.. while me n jake threw the football & he tought me how to throw spiral.. dun be jealous. hehe.. thenn he started laughing at me and i couldnt really breathe from laughing.. bcuz my 2 fingers on my right hand started shaking and wouldnt stop andd it was just funny. ahahaha.. but now they stopped... thank god. uh.. london had attacks 2day.. and yes i was def. there 8-).. thenn we went on the trampoline w/ meya n allie ..it was fun.. then i came in & just sat around.. my family is watching hitch but i dun wanna watch itt.. i only like 1 part when his face gits all puffy :) hahahaha.. wellll im gonna go find sumthing 2 do.. byebye!*

hi! well.. this morning was fun.. i was at toni jos n i layed around n stuff w/ every1.. then went on the trampoline w/ ppl.. & made food? then i eventually left at 4. i think im gonna move in with them :) haha.. well then jake picked me up n we got becca time hortons n we came home.. n i cooked dinner w/ becca & waited for my mom to get home from robinson w/ allie.. & we ate dinner.. jake went back 2 akron for a couple days.. n i didnt do anything 2night at all :( but i think im gonna stop writin cuz i have nothing 2 write. later onnnn*

hi.. well  im at tonis but 2day we got up n went inside from the tent. hahah.. then she fell back asleep and i went to clean and got online.. then at like 3:30 my aunts n cousins came over n  swam and had a cookout. thenn i took a shower & came here.. we went to the paRk for a lil bit but it smelled bad so i caught lightening bugs :) then we came back here & lit off fireworks ..n kirsten got home n her friends came over like angela mary n shawna.. uh well were just sitting here now, so ill write in here 2moro. k bye*

hi loves. today was quite fun! lol.. i woke up n went to churchh & some lady passed out and there were ppl just like walking down the isle in the middle of mass and me and becca were like "are those ppl supposed to be there?" hahaha.. oh myy. thenn toni jo came over after around like 2:30 & we swam and layed out.. and went on the trampoline.. then went dinner & got on here n stuff. then went swimming some moree n went downstairs w/ becca n her & played pool & stuff.. then toni jo was petting chloe and she was like "i like your dog, can i take her home?" and pet her again, and then chloe bit her.. hahahahahahahaha. my chest hurt from laughing.. me n becca were dying. then we watched this one part on the incredibles.. "that was totally wicked!" hahahaha. ohh my.then jason came over and we played basketball i soo beat him badly he was def. embarassed. haha jk. 8-)  umthen we watched fireworks and stuff.. then went night swimming and palyed games in the pool 8-). fun times. so okay.. me and toni are camping out so bye!!*

hi! well tonight i went to toronto fireworks w/ my brother and his sister (paige) ..they were real good. we sat behind timmy.. and more of my brothers friends. now paige is here cuz jake has to watch her for a little bit.. umm i have nothingg to write about so im gonna go! xoxo*you kno.

--hmm.. well my mom woke me up at like 9 this morning looking for a walky talky thing for dubois and i was about to punch her in her face =). then i fell back asleep til like 11? i dunno what im doing today.. i might call nicolette becuz i havent seen her in forever! & toni jo might come night swimming but i dunno. i think im going to tonis house on the fourth of july becuz were not going down to the river  for fireworks =( cuz they hadd to switch them down there instead of bellview. im gonna go swimming now or play basketball i think =) so ill write in here later if i do anything.. byeee

hi! im typing this quick bcuz i keep getting kicked off bcuz the laptops internet is screwed up =) but uh i wrote in here lastnight at tonis so ill go from this morning i woke up at like 6:48 then 7:48 then 8:48 then 9:48 ..haha thats "my new lucky number" says somebOdy x3. uh then me n toni talked on the phone w/ sum1 n then also i needed to pee n bubba had all the toliet paper in her hand?! so i took it from her and she chased me down the hallway. hahahaha. she scares me. umm then i came home and tommy was here w/ allie.. then i cleaned & stuff.. & got ready real quick n went to drive around w/ allie then stopped to see my dad at the funeral home and stuff.. but becca wants me to go outside on the trampoline now and i might swim with becca meya and allie.. so k bye!*

hii! well im at tonis right now. but anyways today i went driving w/ allie then nicole came over & we swam in the rain for a little bit then came inside w/ meya and allie n katie then they went to buy hair dye for allies hair and picked up jeanne! then thhey came back n me n nicole watched the dye allies hair and stuff then she eventually left =( and i took a shower & straightened my hair then came heree we were supposed to camp out in her back yard but it rained! boo the rain. uh well we wwent to dylan pauls :-P hes the sweetest 9 year old ever. we ordered dominos & sat around and talked.. then he just like left and me n toni came back up here n got on here, but i think shes gettin on now so bye!* xoxo

hi! last night i got home around 2:30 thank god! i missed every1 very very much. uh then i got online but no one was on so me n becca went downstairs to bed.. n i woke up at like 8 in the morning, i have no clue why so i went back to bed til like 11 then i woke up n sat around & eventually i unpacked, then tk came over & so did toni jo at like 2.. we all swam & stuff like that for like an hour n then me n toni walked to wendys & we were "attempting" to talk on the phone and the guy at wendys was like taking all of our money? so we just took it back and got our food and left. then we walked to shaynas for like 2 minutes and said hi then left and sat on the curb and ate fries? haha. were dorks.. then we walked back to riesbecks.. but we didnt have enough strength to walk the rest of the way & we didnt wanna walk the back way so we called my mom to come get us.. thenn we came back and got in the pool eventually.. i think thats about all? toni left at idunno what time but it was around 9:30 or 10? yeah.. well i might go to nicoles 2moro so im real excited. but i dont have any other plans yet =) next weekend = me and toni are camping out in her backyardddddddd.. woohoo 8-) & theres fireworks going off somewhere near my house, theyre attractive. k well bye! xoxo *rachel

hey.. well today i swam!! woohoo,  then i layed out and i have real dark tanlines now, eh 8-) tehn i went to the store and brrought bread & stuff then came back and ate.. then everyone else came home and we sat around, eventually me jessie and becca went to the store and we rode our bikes there (thats the cool thing to do in hilton head) 8-) and when we got there me n becca got icecream n jessie got a slushie cuz i was reall hot. then we came home and on the way back jessie fell off her bike aahahaha funniest thing everrr but shes sexy :) i think then i played scrabble with my aunt and becca =) k well im waiting for my food to come home and im STARVING i didnt eat today.. and its 7:05 now so bye* xoxo

hey. i just got real hyper and excited.. im not to sure why though. i cannot wait til i get homeeee! i miss everyone alot :( wow. im talking to jerry and we have like the same favorites.. geeze lol.but um tonight we ate dinner then got ready & went to sea pines again and i got a toering and 2 books.. sisterhood of the traveling pants and another book but i forget what its called.. um then we went to harbour town and me jess al n bec were gonna go to the top of the lighthouse but it was closed so we walked around and then me jess n becca were standing in the hallway and these 3 boys tried to pick us up n they were like why u buggin.. so we just walked past them n they were like nah were messin.. hahaha theyre gay :-! umm.. then we came home n my mom n my two aunts went to the store real quick and us kids just stayed here.. then we played tripoley.. and okay i suddenly dont wanna type in here so bye =) *

hello! well i get home tuesdayy! today in steubenville it was like 117 in the sun.. uh! everytime we go on vacation we miss the nice weather.. then when i get home tuesday its supposed to storm for the rest of the week? blah. well me and toni have sick plans for wednesday and the rain better not ruin them! okay today i got up and jessie and allie were leaving, trying to unlock the door with this bar thing so they told me to get up & do it.. so i got up n they left, and my mom and my two aunts took my other aunt to the airport.. then they got home and we ate lunch then went to the pool again.. and i didnt even wanna try to swim. but guess who swam last night with jess n becca.. meeee! but im not gonna try again  it was too risky :) but uh i already had a tan so all i did was get darker.. :-! well jessie didnt wana get burnt so me and her came home and she got in the shower while i was on here then when she was done i got in the shower.. n allie and becca then came home.. and now beccas in the shower.. but i think im gonna stop writing in here, bye. xoxo
